    "Health Savings Account-Eligible High Deductible Health Plan",
    "Medically Underserved Areas",
    "Tax Credit"
  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "For taxable years beginning 1/1/2026, establishes a tiered nonrefundable tax credit for qualified taxpayer insurers that offer one or more federally qualified health savings account\u2011eligible high deductible health plans in the State, under certain conditions, and increasing the tax credit to incentivize more plans being written in rural medically underserved areas of the State.  Requires qualified taxpayer insurers to match up to a certain amount of a policyholder's first-time contribution into a health savings account.  Sunsets 12/31/2030."
    }
  ],
